## Starting Moodle with Docker Compose

1. Open a terminal and navigate to the Moodle docker directory:
   
	cd "/home/simon/Desktop/Learning Management System Academy/learning-platform/docker/moodle"

2. Start the containers in detached mode:
   
	docker-compose up -d

3. Access Moodle in your browser:
   
	http://localhost:8081/

If you need to stop the containers:

	docker-compose down
Activate environment

source "/home/simon/Desktop/Learning Management System Academy/dev_env/bin/activate"